edu.stanford.math.plex4.homology.barcodes
Class IntBarcodeCollection

java.lang.Object
  edu.stanford.math.plex4.homology.barcodes.IntBarcodeCollection

public class IntBarcodeCollection
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements functionality for storing a collection of barcodes. It is designed to be the output of a persistent homology or cohomology algorithm so that it contains the persistence intervals at each dimension.

Author:
Andrew Tausz
